      <title>今年开局艰难，交易员纷纷抛售新兴市场</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-17/traders-ditch-emerging-markets-in-rocky-start-of-the-year</link>
      <description><![CDATA[2025 年初，投资者纷纷从新兴市场撤资，因为他们在衡量唐纳德·特朗普 (Donald Trump) 下周重返白宫后，他的威胁中有多少会变成政策。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-17/traders-ditch-emerging-markets-in-rocky-start-of-the-year</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 17 Jan 2025 18:05:33 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
